        <heading>1945.  Revocation of an offer of reward made to the public</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 1945.  Revocation of an offer of reward made to the public
An offer of reward made to the public may be revoked before completion of the requested act, provided the revocation is made by the same or an equally effective means as the offer.</p>
        </content>
        <authorialNote marker="source">
          <p>Source: https://www.legis.la.gov/legis/Law.aspx?d=109194</p>
